graph TD
    User([User]) -->|Telegram Message| TelegramAPI[Telegram API]
    TelegramAPI -->|Webhook| Main[main.py: Flask App]
    
    subgraph "Application Core (Stateful & Self-Learning)"
        Main -->|handle_request chat_id| Middleware[middleware.py: Stateful Logic Hub]
        
        Middleware <-->|Load/Update Session| Memory[(memory.py: Situation Model)]
        
        Middleware -->|perception_simulate| Perception[Perception: Intent/Entities/Class]
        Perception -->|TMR JSON| Middleware
        
        Middleware -->|deliberation_query_kg| Deliberation[Deliberation: Logic Engine]
        Deliberation -->|query_by_ontology| Knowledge[knowledge.py: KG Interface]
        
        Knowledge -->|read| KGData[(data/knowledge_graph.json)]
        Knowledge -->|Verified Facts| Deliberation
        
        %% Dynamic Ingestion Loop
        Deliberation -->|Cache Miss: Trigger| DynIngest[tools/dynamic_ingest.py]
        DynIngest -->|Triple-Threat Execution| IngestPipeline
        KGData -.->|New Nodes Merged| Knowledge
        
        Deliberation -->|Consolidated TMR + Facts| Middleware
        
        Middleware -->|produce_final_response| ResponseGen[Action Rendering]
        ResponseGen -->|Prompt with Verified Facts| LLM[Google GenAI Gemini]
        LLM -->|Natural Language| ResponseGen
        ResponseGen -->|Final Text| Middleware
    end
    
    subgraph IngestPipeline ["Triple-Threat Ingestion Pipeline"]
        OSM[OpenStreetMap: Physicality] -->|ingest_osm.py| RawData[Raw Nodes]
        RawData -->|ingest_enrich.py| Enforcer[Enrichment Layer]
        Enforcer -->|Pillar 2: OneMap API| OneMap[onemap_client.py]
        Enforcer -->|Pillar 3: LLM Context| LLM_Enrich[LLM Reasoning]
        OneMap -.->|Fallback| LLM_Enrich
        LLM_Enrich -->|merge_kg.py| KGData
    end
    
    Middleware -->|Response Text| Main
    Main -->|HTTP 200| TelegramAPI
    TelegramAPI -->|Message| User
    
    classDef core fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
    class Middleware,Main,Perception,Deliberation,ResponseGen,Knowledge core;
    classDef data fill:#dfd,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
    class KGData,Memory,Ontology data;
    classDef external fill:#ddf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
    class User,TelegramAPI,LLM,OSM external;
